<i>Posted by Gersh on 10-24-2001 10:46 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>** Shift Right Clicking your buff icons will remove the buffs<br />
<br />
** The group mini window can only be brought up when you are currently in a group, after you bring it up however it will not dissapear after you leave the group, or relog. Thus allowing you to place and adjust your mini group window to a permanent position so you don't have to use the big bulky Group interface.<br />
<br />
** Clicking Critcal shot 2 times will switch to a normal shot<br />
<br />
** Whatever arrow is at the top of your inventory when you draw a shot will be the arrow used regardless if you move another stack above before you release the shot<br />
<br />
** Reserve 50% sta for emergencies or fights you are unsure you will win, generally 50% sta and 30% health is all you need to get enough of a lead on a mob in order to escape.<br />
<br />
** Dying will remove the Task you are currently working on (mini quest for tradeskills)<br />
<br />
** Do not use mid over the shoulder camera view when being auto followed by a large PC (Troll, Firblogs) they will occasionally blot out your character and most of the screen<br />
<br />
** Using the scroll wheel while mouselooking in over ther shoulder view will zoom in and out on your character<font face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
