<i>Posted by Ghan on 11-01-2001 02:45 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>The /stick command can be used on MOBs as well as player characters. It makes casters with a tendency to ping pong MOBs much less annoying.<br />
<br />
It also comes in handy with styles that must be used from the side or back of a MOB. /Stick, then use the strafe keys to swing around to the side or back.</p>
